msgid "Module for creating and customizing reports across all system modules."
msgstr "Module permettant de creer et de personnaliser des rapports sur l'ensemble des modules du systeme."

msgid ""
"Removed redundant fields attributes superseded by form_class on report CRUD "
"views, standardized first-party import groups, and added docstrings for "
"pylint compliance."
msgstr ""
"Suppression des attributs de champs redondants remplaces par form_class dans "
"les vues CRUD des rapports, standardisation des imports et ajout de "
"docstrings pour la conformite pylint."

msgid ""
"Report forms aligned with HorillaModelForm layout: field_order and Meta."
"fields = \"__all__\" with Meta.exclude; folder and column HTMX unchanged."
msgstr ""
"Formulaires de rapports alignes sur le layout HorillaModelForm : field_order "
"et Meta.fields avec Meta.exclude ; HTMX du dossier et de la colonne inchange."

msgid ""
"Release 1.10: reports ship under contrib with app label reports. Cross-app "
"report wiring, ContentType references, namespaces, and registrations updated "
"for the contrib naming scheme."
msgstr ""
"Version 1.10 : les rapports sont integres sous contrib avec le label "
"d'application reports. Cablage des rapports inter-applications, references "
"ContentType, espaces de noms et enregistrements mis a jour."

msgid ""
"Improved report compatibility with dashboard multi-widget support, enhanced "
"chart_value_field handling, and minor stability improvements for report "
"rendering and filter processing."
msgstr ""
"Amelioration de la compatibilite des rapports avec le support multi-widgets "
"du tableau de bord, gestion amelioree de chart_value_field et ameliorations "
"mineures de stabilite."

msgid ""
"Added support for advanced chart types including Treemap, Area charts, "
"Heatmaps, Sankey diagrams, and Radar charts. Improved compatibility with the "
"new visualization and analytics framework."
msgstr ""
"Ajout du support pour les types de graphiques avances incluant Treemap, "
"graphiques en aire, cartes thermiques, diagrammes de Sankey et graphiques "
"radar. Compatibilite amelioree avec le nouveau framework de visualisation."

msgid ""
"Migrated from Django AppConfig to Horilla AppLauncher and and replacedDjango "
"utilities with horilla.utils.decorators, horilla.utils.translation,and "
"horilla.shortcuts where applicable."
msgstr ""
"Migration de Django AppConfig vers Horilla AppLauncher et remplacement des "
"utilitaires Django par horilla.utils.decorators, horilla.utils.translation "
"et horilla.shortcuts selon le cas."

